The paper deals with algorithms for simplifying flow networks on directed planar graphs, which involves topics such as graph theory, computational geometry, and numerical analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
